CustomField.description: Used with Eloqua integration - when a contact is marked "unmarketable" in Eloqua, it will pass the information to Salesforce. We will date/time stamp the "eloqua unmarketable" field on the Contact record and excluded any "Unmarketable not equal to blank" from being sent back to Eloqua through integration on Eloqua side.
CustomField.label: Mktg Automation Unmarketable Date
